## Loopr Integration

This project uses Loopr for Ralph Loop orchestration. Key files:

- `.loopr/PROMPT_plan.md` - Planning phase prompt
- `.loopr/PROMPT_build.md` - Build phase prompt
- `.loopr/AGENTS.md` - Operational notes for agents
- `.loopr/specs/*` - Specifications for features
- `@IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md` - Current implementation plan

### Running Loops

```bash
# Generate implementation plan
loopr plan

# Build from plan
loopr build
```

